     V* 09/05/19  V5R1   BMA Corrected eval $$SVAR
     V* 19/06/19  V5R1   BMA Get Targa attribute without p_rxval and p_rxlate
     V* 25/06/19  V5R1   AD  Move entry from £INIZI to main
